        <text>CM_CashReceipt.CREDIT_CHECK_PENDING = 0
CM_CashReceipt.CREDIT_CHECK_APPROVED = 1
CM_CashReceipt.CREDIT_CHECK_REJECTED = 2
CM_CashReceipt.CREDIT_CANCEL_PENDING  = 3
CM_CashReceipt.CREDIT_CANCEL_APPROVED  = 4
CM_CashReceipt.PAID  = 5
CM_CashReceipt.CREDIT_CANCEL_MANUAL = 6

*NOTE* These are intended to only be used by cash APIs
NAVKC1 04/07/2024 CR 64834 TASK 64845
